# 📈 FinAnalyzer Pro - API Configuration

# Get your Gemini API Key from: https://aistudio.google.com/
# This key is required for earnings analysis, sentiment scoring, and the real-time AI analyst.
VITE_API_KEY="YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY"

# Configuration Note:
# 1. Rename this file to .env
# 2. Replace YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY with your actual key.
# 3. Ensure .env is never committed to version control.
